Properties summary

Activities
Activities

Required. Activities that belong to the pipeline.
Datasets
Datasets

Optional. List of datasets to be used by activities defined in the pipeline. This can be used to define datasets that are specific to this pipeline and not defined within the datafactory. Datasets defined within this pipeline can only be used by this pipeline and cannot be shared.
Description
Description

Optional. Item description.
End
End

Optional. The end time of the pipeline. The start and end time can both be empty to create a pipeline; they must both have values to set an active period for the pipeline and one cannot have a value if the other does not.
ErrorMessage
ErrorMessage

Optional. Error in processing pipeline request.
ExpirationTime
ExpirationTime

Optional. Duration of time after creation for which the pipeline is valid and should remain provisioned. The pipeline will be deleted automatically once it reaches the expiration time if it does not have any active or pending runs.
HubName
HubName

Optional. The name of the Hub that this pipeline belongs to.
IsPaused
IsPaused

Optional. The status of the pipline. Pipeline is paused when boolean is set to true.
PipelineMode
PipelineMode

Optional. The method of scheduling runs for the pipeline. Must be one of PipelineMode.
ProvisioningState
ProvisioningState

Optional. The provisioning state of the pipeline.
RuntimeInfo
RuntimeInfo

Optional. Pipeline runtime information.
Start
Start

Optional. The start time of the pipeline. The start and end time can both be empty to create a pipeline; they must both have values to set an active period for the pipeline and one cannot have a value if the other does not.
